g outside which means the new season is just around the corner. And so do fresh ideas and inspiration. Each and every Visual Composer showcase is intended to make you feel that way. <strong>#madeinvc</strong></p><p>But this one is a worth-reading knowledge-packed piece containing the best practices on how to utilize the most popular features of the plugin for a specific industry. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vce-row-container\"><div class=\"vce-row vce-element--has-background vce-row--col-gap-30 vce-row-content--top\" data-vce-full-width=\"true\" id=\"el-56e26583\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-56e26583\"><div class=\"vce-content-background-container\"></div><div class=\"vce-row-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\"><div class=\"vce-col vce-col--md-auto vce-col--xs-1 vce-col--xs-last vce-col--xs-first vce-col--sm-last vce-col--sm-first vce-col--md-last vce-col--lg-last vce-col--xl-last vce-col--md-first vce-col--lg-first vce-col--xl-first\" id=\"el-e2f530a7\"><div class=\"vce-col-inner\" data-vce-do-apply=\"border margin background  el-e2f530a7\"><div class=\"vce-col-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\" data-vce-do-apply=\"padding el-e2f530a7\"><div class=\"vce-single-image-container vce-single-image--align-center\"><div class=\"vce vce-single-image-wrapper\" id=\"el-1e148b3c\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-1e148b3c\"><figure><a href=\"https://www.heartfish.io/\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"vce-single-image-inner vce-single-image--absolute\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.9524%; width: 840px;\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"vce-single-image\" width=\"840\" height=\"470\" src=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/heartfish--840x470.png\" srcset=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/heartfish--320x179.png 320w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/heartfish--480x269.png 480w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/heartfish--800x448.png 800w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/heartfish--840x470.png 840w\" data-img-src=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/heartfish-.png\" alt=\"Heartfish website\" title=\"Heartfish website\" /></a><figcaption hidden=\"\"></figcaption></figure></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vce-row-container\" data-vce-boxed-width=\"true\"><div class=\"vce-row vce-row--col-gap-30 vce-row-content--top\" id=\"el-76b1624a\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-76b1624a\"><div class=\"vce-content-background-container\"></div><div class=\"vce-row-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\"><div class=\"vce-col vce-col--md-100p vce-col--xs-1 vce-col--xs-last vce-col--xs-first vce-col--sm-last vce-col--sm-first vce-col--md-last vce-col--lg-last vce-col--xl-last vce-col--md-first vce-col--lg-first vce-col--xl-first\" id=\"el-6c621fa8\"><div class=\"vce-col-inner\" data-vce-do-apply=\"border margin background  el-6c621fa8\"><div class=\"vce-col-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\" data-vce-do-apply=\"padding el-6c621fa8\"><div class=\"vce-text-block\"><div class=\"vce-text-block-wrapper vce\" id=\"el-3ce1e8e2\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-3ce1e8e2\"><h2><a href=\"https://www.heartfish.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Heartfish</a></h2><p>Heartfish is a single idea that emerged onto a fitness mobile app. This is also a great example of how well the design of the above-fold part can bring together various content types <em>(like Shadow Button element from the <a href=\"https://visualcomposer.com/features/visual-composer-hub/\">Visual Composer Hub</a> and custom graphics)</em> to tell the story behind the company.</p><p>But the Heartfish app is also about applying a fresh perspective to an ordinary feature highlight. Instead of creating a section or even a separate page dedicated to features of the product, this company uses a Timeline With Icons content element <em>(also available in Visual Composer Hub)</em>.</p><p>Another powerful solution of the plugin to support your app business is a Phone Mockup element, so you can display your app design to website visitors. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vce-row-container\"><div class=\"vce-row vce-element--has-background vce-row--col-gap-30 vce-row-content--top\" data-vce-full-width=\"true\" id=\"el-0be5924a\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-0be5924a\"><div class=\"vce-content-background-container\"></div><div class=\"vce-row-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\"><div class=\"vce-col vce-col--md-auto vce-col--xs-1 vce-col--xs-last vce-col--xs-first vce-col--sm-last vce-col--sm-first vce-col--md-last vce-col--lg-last vce-col--xl-last vce-col--md-first vce-col--lg-first vce-col--xl-first\" id=\"el-2cc0034d\"><div class=\"vce-col-inner\" data-vce-do-apply=\"border margin background  el-2cc0034d\"><div class=\"vce-col-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\" data-vce-do-apply=\"padding el-2cc0034d\"><div class=\"vce-single-image-container vce-single-image--align-center\"><div class=\"vce vce-single-image-wrapper\" id=\"el-b5fb8525\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-b5fb8525\"><figure><a href=\"https://bluesoft.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"vce-single-image-inner vce-single-image--absolute\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.9524%; width: 840px;\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"vce-single-image\" width=\"840\" height=\"470\" src=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bluesoft-840x470.png\" srcset=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bluesoft-320x179.png 320w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bluesoft-480x269.png 480w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bluesoft-800x448.png 800w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bluesoft-840x470.png 840w\" data-img-src=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bluesoft.png\" alt=\"BlueSoft website\" title=\"BlueSoft website\" /></a><figcaption hidden=\"\"><